The shop is located right at Hang Xanh roundabout, next to HUB university. The shop has 3 floors equipped with air conditioning, simple but luxurious decoration with 2 main colors: white and coffee brown. On the ground floor, right at the entrance is the order counter, the shop serves coffee and tea at quite competitive prices, cheaper than Hightland and Phuc Long with equivalent or even higher quality. The ground floor and first floor are always crowded, mostly young people, the ground floor is a bit noisier than the first floor. The layout style of the floors is quite similar with 2 main colors, however the 2nd and 3rd floors are decorated in a more Zen style and are completely quiet, probably well soundproofed so they are completely separate from the world. Outside, the decoration is very elegant and polite, it is the only place where smoking is allowed, and is equipped with a deodorizer so even though the space is closed, it does not smell bad and does not affect the next table. Silence is strictly respected. I really like this at Trung Nguyen Legend Cafe, it is also a unique and unique point that I highly appreciate here.
